<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بَابُ الدُّعَاءِ وَالصَّلَاةِ مِنْ آخِرِ اللَّيْلِ وَقَالَ ﴿كَانُوا قَلِيلا مِنَ اللَّيْلِ مَا يَهْجَعُونَ﴾<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٥٣⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أَيْ مَا يَنَامُونَ ﴿وَبِالأَسْحَارِ هُمْ يَسْتَغْفِرُونَ﴾<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>